com.intel.icecp.module.httpbridge

Class HttpBridge_Module.HttpPoolExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.concurrent.AbstractExecutorService
      • java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor
        • com.intel.icecp.module.httpbridge.HttpBridge_Module.HttpPoolExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Executor, ExecutorService
    Enclosing class:
    HttpBridge_Module

    public class HttpBridge_Module.HttpPoolExecutor
extends ThreadPoolExecutor
    Extend the ThreadPoolExecutor that we use for starting the http connection threads. This allows us to override the beforeExecute() method and set the threads context class loader to our module loader. This is required to support ServiceLoaders that use their default ExtensionLoaders. We set our threads context loader to the ModuleClassLoader so that the ServiceLoader providers can be found.
